Retrieves the current cost for calcium c.name: Retrieves the current cost for calcium chloride.
Retrieves the current cost for calcium c.sql:
DECLARE @needle NVARCHAR(100) = UPPER(?);
SELECT TOP 1 ITEMNMBR, ITEMDESC, CURRCOST, STNDCOST
FROM IV00101
WHERE UPPER(ITEMNMBR) = @needle
    OR UPPER(REPLACE(ITEMNMBR, ' ', '')) = @needle
    OR UPPER(ITEMDESC) LIKE '%' + @needle + '%'
    OR UPPER(ITEMDESC) LIKE '%CALCIUM%CHLORIDE%'
ORDER BY CASE
    WHEN UPPER(ITEMNMBR) = @needle THEN 0
    WHEN UPPER(REPLACE(ITEMNMBR, ' ', '')) = @needle THEN 1
    ELSE 2
END, ITEMNMBR;
